  "detailed_description": "Smokey the toad is not your average amphibian. With a propane-fueled weed burner in hand, he charges into battle against a relentless force of hostile frogs in a race war that threatens to tear his world apart. Get ready to take on the challenge of 30 heart-pumping levels across 5 intense environments. And with power-ups and secrets to discover, every level is full of surprises.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEncounter fast-paced action, eccentric characters, and intense boss battles that will keep you on the edge of your seat! But don't worry, Smokey has a few tricks up his sleeve. With special attacks like blasting forward as a ball of fire and zooming across the sky with his flamethrower-jetpack combo, nothing can stop this determined toad.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith thrilling gameplay, exciting battles, and an engaging story, Smokey's adventure is one you won't want to miss! Get ready to save the world and become a hero in this thrilling 2D shooter game.",
  "about_the_game": "Smokey the toad is not your average amphibian. With a propane-fueled weed burner in hand, he charges into battle against a relentless force of hostile frogs in a race war that threatens to tear his world apart. Get ready to take on the challenge of 30 heart-pumping levels across 5 intense environments. And with power-ups and secrets to discover, every level is full of surprises.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEncounter fast-paced action, eccentric characters, and intense boss battles that will keep you on the edge of your seat! But don't worry, Smokey has a few tricks up his sleeve. With special attacks like blasting forward as a ball of fire and zooming across the sky with his flamethrower-jetpack combo, nothing can stop this determined toad.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith thrilling gameplay, exciting battles, and an engaging story, Smokey's adventure is one you won't want to miss! Get ready to save the world and become a hero in this thrilling 2D shooter game.",
